  "text": "The measured rate of oxygen consumption for B. subtilis is in the range of 0.5-2 × 10 6 molecules s −1 cell −1 [CITATION_1] . Oxygen concentration at the airsuspension interface is less than 10 mg l −1 ª 10 5 molecules mm −3",
